{"tid":1447661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雖然今晚大家好傷痛，但唔好放過內鬼e粒核彈","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:06:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:05:19.000Z","uid":107681,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ecf00de4cac7fd75b123b6ae2f7597b4989456af","tid":1447661,"uid":107681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:06:38.000Z","msg":"e粒核彈無論文宣又好，記者會都好都要好好發大佢<br />\n其一，合理懷疑大量暴力衝擊行為都係政府有意派內鬼制造<br />\n其二，內鬼於示威者內煽動其他人做出暴力行動<br />\n要全方位發大e粒核彈，唔可以好似元朗咁比政府淡化，內鬼有冇做進行以上既行為，政府係絕對拎唔出證據證明，所以好似元朗一樣，係可能解得到。<br />\n律師都要研究下，係法庭有冇可能作為合理疑點教義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0f3ebc5ca9f4e9b0a78dbb6ad8a0fedee76677","tid":1447661,"uid":107681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:08:33.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"2fb7f45a59d0ab97d6bdf0dd037d1096c838de58","tid":1447661,"uid":107681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:08:43.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"1973aeeb19c1949879f04c371289e388d20a2b1a","tid":1447661,"uid":90012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:11:48.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"008c82d55a49d94489f06d9f2011a99eb934e1ab","tid":1447661,"uid":107681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:26:53.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"43a61c17551a407b3647b10ec621b0a2af05e055","tid":1447661,"uid":107681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:05:19.000Z","msg":"721812"}]}